title: What's The Best Cereal? ft. Justine Sterling
description:
Today, we're joined by the editor and chief of Sporked, Justine Sterling, to discuss: What's The Best Cereal?
Sporked is Mythical's new website dedicated to helping you find the best food on the shelves! They're taste testing everything from oat milks to spicy chips and sharing their results with you!
Check out Sporked:
